  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Go to any chat or community\r\n2. In the Message field enter a space or a few spaces, send the message\r\n3. Add a reaction to this empty message\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nAll popular messengers are not allowing sending an empty message because they just add a gap between the tread of messages.\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n1. The empty message is sent\r\n2. The reaction is added\r\n<img width=\"1305\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/14942081/190055345-0590366a-6954-413c-9519-de3054dce617.png\">\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: https://ci.status.im/job/status-desktop/job/platforms/job/macos/216/\r\n- Operating System: macOS Monterey\r\n\r\n",
